"을 클릭하세요."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:69
msgid ""
"Open the :ref:`Cloudflare Turnstile <website/spam_protection/cloudflare>` "
"page, copy the :guilabel:`Site Key`, and paste it into the :guilabel:`CF "
"Site Key` field in Odoo."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Cloudflare Turnstile <website/spam_protection/cloudflare>`\\ 페이지를 "
"열고\\ :guilabel:`사이트 키`\\ 를 복사하여 Odoo의\\ :guilabel:`CF 사이트 키"
"`\\ 필드에 붙여넣으세요."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:71
msgid ""
"Open the Cloudflare Turnstile page, copy the :guilabel:`Secret Key`, and "
